{
  "stem": "1641.5",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I'll be quiet like a mouse.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "So that was one little story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And then the other-- other thing what happened is that of course, people started to lose their teeth because malnutrition, lack of all the vitamins, all the gums got infected and sore, and swollen, full with puss, and the teeth just fell out.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "They didn't fully fell out till you pull it out yourself because it was-- they were just in the way, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "You just swallowed it, or-- so all the teeth-- it fell out over a six week period, not-- not just in one day.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But every day, you lost one or two teeth.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the whole mouth was-- which was a big problem.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The gums were badly rotting and full with puss.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you managed to get a piece of bread, then it was a major problem.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You had to-- you couldn't swallow it in one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So you had to break it up with your finger into smaller units, and then just make it wet with your saliva, and somehow swallow it, because you couldn't not eat and rotten gums.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was a very difficult situation to be in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that's how it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the dead bodies-- more and more people died.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the stage came that every morning, from the six people, we had to throw out three.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Two or three every morning we had to throw out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they quickly filled it up, because new and new transports arrived from Hungary, from Czechoslovakia, from Romania.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "People were driven to the-- to the Reich.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so we see the new transports coming in, relatively fleshy people, who still have-- who had-- who have eaten something the previous few weeks.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then they died, in turn.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
